## 2. CardArea Translation Standards

- **Scaling:** Card x-position = `(areaWidth / cardCount)`. Use `CARD_LAYOUT` from `UIConstants.js`.
- **Overlap:** When cards exceed slot limit, use "squish" logic — cards overlap but stay centered (see `.card-area-squish` in styles).
- **Z-Index:** Right-hand cards have higher z-index than left.

---

## 3. Math & Scaling Constants

- **Base Card Size:** 71×95px aspect ratio (see `.cursor/context/BALATRO_DESIGN_PRINCIPLES.md`).
- **Mult Order:** Process `+Mult` (additive) before `×Mult` (multiplicative). Same as mechanics rule.
- **Trigger Order:** `Dice → Held Items → Boons (left to right) → Edition Effects`.

---

## 4. Visual & Juice Alignment

- **Shaders / dissolve / juice:** Map to CSS animations or `juice-effects.css` / `balatro-effects.css`.
- **Outlines:** 2px strong outline for pixel-art style (see visual tokens).
- **Dithering:** Use finely dithered backgrounds per style guide.
- **Tooltips (Balatro-style):** Main tooltip shows summary; nested `data-tooltip` on enhancement/tag items shows separate description popup on hover (like Balatro's `detailed_tooltip`). Tooltip must stay visible when hovering into popup content.

